This paper is primarily focused on the security and privacy aspects of Facebook applications, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses user behavior and awareness, which could be categorized under social and information sciences (cs.SI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper touches upon issues related to cybercrime (cs.CY) and social networks (cs.SOC).
